{"tid":1901670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"599C名單單嘢要重視下","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T00:37:52.000Z","uid":74622,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"67afe9d740ffe8d96422b2e98e155748e01c7ac7","tid":1901670,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"599C名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.docdroid.net/qyQL2qb/599c-home-tcpdf.pdf#page=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.docdroid.net%2FqyQL2qb%2F599c-home-tcpdf.pdf%23page%3D6&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=a6774b5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.docdroid.net/qyQL2qb/599c-home-tcpdf.pdf#page=6</a><br />\n<br />\n政府個網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/599c_home_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2F599c_home_tc.pdf&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=fd95c058\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/599c_home_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n 雖然刪咗 但係用上面條Link喺Google 搜尋係會有紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygXL2LX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygXL2LX.jpg&h=5641c964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一條紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?client=firefox-b-d&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2F599c_home_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fclient%3Dfirefox-b-d%26q%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chp.gov.hk%252Ffiles%252Fpdf%252F599c_home_tc.pdf&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=23e0049e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?client=firefox-b-d&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2F599c_home_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】網傳逾 5800 幢強制檢疫大廈名單 18 區元朗佔最多 紀律部隊宿舍有份<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%80%BE-5800-%E5%B9%A2%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA-18-%E5%8D%80%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E4%BD%94%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2580%25BE-5800-%25E5%25B9%25A2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2587%25BA-18-%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E4%25BD%2594%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BD%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=a1a3328f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2580%25BE-5800-%25E5%25B9%25A2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2587%25BA-18-%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E4%25BD%2594%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BD%2F&h=79ff94fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%80%BE-5800-%E5%B9%A2%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA-18-%E5%8D%80%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E4%BD%94%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屯門區議員何杏梅向《立場新聞》確認，流傳名單是由民政事務署提供</span></span>，她指出曾有當區居民擔心自己居住的大廈是否有人由大陸回港接受強制檢疫，因此便代居民向民政事務署查詢，其職員便以電子方式提供有關名單，讓區議員參考。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署回覆《立場》查詢時指出，未有正面回應名單的真偽，只是稱正整合相關的大廈名單，以期盡快於網頁公布。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以自己決定信唔信</span>"},{"pid":"db5c67fb053fed7962a2c8b8d3fc6a0c5e4ec4a1","tid":1901670,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deabf6a5a09e5686f40a246443b3fa30e32e71be","tid":1901670,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"其實大家都心裡有數啦<br />\n木馬屠城已經開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/1779310_713527455346330_887712826_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_oc=AQnuiyzvqDiuc48p8MXLiOE13iEnN6n1SmEKe435LbtWolrRCbmPuCYXReRno5F-DsQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ea6118407b62db69ac00785b0f1b30c0&amp;oe=5F0091FA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F1779310_713527455346330_887712826_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D2d5d41%26_nc_oc%3DAQnuiyzvqDiuc48p8MXLiOE13iEnN6n1SmEKe435LbtWolrRCbmPuCYXReRno5F-DsQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dea6118407b62db69ac00785b0f1b30c0%26oe%3D5F0091FA&h=ac19ab49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5186102bf46ad21a8776259d4a89fe54f7d1d182","tid":1901670,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deabf6a5a09e5686f40a246443b3fa30e32e71be","tid":1901670,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"其實大家都心裡有數啦<br />\n木馬屠城已經開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/1779310_713527455346330_887712826_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_oc=AQnuiyzvqDiuc48p8MXLiOE13iEnN6n1SmEKe435LbtWolrRCbmPuCYXReRno5F-DsQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ea6118407b62db69ac00785b0f1b30c0&amp;oe=5F0091FA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F1779310_713527455346330_887